The paper deals with distributed sensor localization, which is a topic related to networked systems and communication. Therefore, cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves algorithms and signal processing, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper uses mathematical analysis and optimization techniques, which could be classified under cs.MA (Mathematical Software).
